content: Yes, Swiss Skydiver's victory at the 2020 Preakness Stakes was remarkable and has further increased her fan following. She has proven herself to be a talented and determined horse, with multiple graded stakes wins throughout 2020. She has also challenged male horses and held her own against them, further cementing her status as one of the best in her division. Keep an eye out for her in future races, as she may continue to surprise and impress horse racing enthusiasts.
